Sentencas: An eigenvalue problem arising from the study of gas dynamics in a loaded tubular solid oxide fuel cell is considered.
Titulo: On some eigenvalue problems in fuel-cell dynamics

Sentencas: An asymptotic theory from which the equations are derived is reviewed, and the results of analysis on the small and large parameter asymptotics are presented.
Titulo: On some eigenvalue problems in fuel-cell dynamics

Sentencas: These results suggest an interesting and hitherto unknown property of a class of Sturm-Liouville problems in which the first eigenvalue approaches zero but subsequent ones approach infinity as a parameter approaches zero.
Titulo: On some eigenvalue problems in fuel-cell dynamics

Sentencas: This was first discovered numerically and later confirmed asymptotically and rigorously.
Titulo: On some eigenvalue problems in fuel-cell dynamics
